      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "[REDACTED] OSI, Kirtland Air Force Base (KAFB), Albuquerque, New Mexico, on 4/26/64, advised that he cannot explain the observations described by [REDACTED] at Socorro, New Mexico.",
