    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "[REDACTED] advised that he and [REDACTED] had examined the site at Socorro, New Mexico, and interviewed [REDACTED]. They were impressed by [REDACTED] sincerity. They noted no radio activity at the site. They cannot explain [REDACTED] observations. He did learn that the New Mexico Institute of Mining and Technology at Socorro does some blasting in its work, however, their blasting is not in the area of this incident.",
